{"name": "minio-sync-tool", "metadata": {"name": "minio-sync-tool", "version": "0.1.0", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": "https://zalogit2.zing.vn/nlp/kilm/ai-platform/minio-sync-tool", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["minio", "tqdm"], "summary": "A package for synchronizing and uploading repositories with MinIO.", "upload_time": 1735527344}, "documentation": ["# MinIO Sync Tool\n\nMinIO Sync Tool is a Python package that simplifies repository synchronization and uploads between local storage and MinIO. It provides an easy-to-use command-line interface for managing files in MinIO buckets.\n\n---\n\n## Features\n\n- Synchronize a repository from MinIO to local storage.\n- Upload a repository from local storage to MinIO.\n- Command-line interface for quick and easy usage.\n\n---\n\n## Usage\n\nThe package provides a CLI tool called sync_minio_repo with the following commands:\n\n### Environment\n\n```bash\nexport MINIO_URL=...\nexport MINIO_ACCESS_KEY=...\nexport MINIO_SECRET_KEY=...\nexport MINIO_SECURE=false # true/false\n```\n\n### Synchronize Repository from MinIO to Local\n\n```bash\nminio_sync_tool sync_repo \\\n    --bucket my-bucket \\\n    --prefix my-repo/ \\\n    --dest ./local-repo \\\n    --version \"version-name\"\n```\n\n**Arguments:**\n\n* `--bucket`: Name of the MinIO bucket containing the repository.\n\n* `--prefix`: Prefix (folder path) in the bucket to sync.\n\n* `--dest`: Local directory where the repository will be synchronized.\n\n* `--version`: Version of the repository to sync.\n\n### Upload Repository from Local to MinIO\n\n```bash\nminio_sync_tool upload_repo \\\n    --bucket my-bucket \\\n    --prefix my-repo/ \\\n    --source ./local-repo\n    --version \"version-name\"\n```\n\n**Arguments:**\n\n* `--bucket`: Name of the MinIO bucket where the repository will be uploaded.\n\n* `--prefix`: Prefix (folder path) in the bucket to upload to.\n\n* `--source`: Local directory containing the repository to upload.\n\n* `--version`: Version name of the repository.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "minio_sync_tool.utils", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "minio_sync_tool.utils.calculate_multipart_etag", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "file_path", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "part_size", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Calculate the multipart ETag for a given file.\n\n```\nparam file_path\n\nPath to the file\n\nparam part_size\n\nSize of each part in bytes\n\nreturn\n\nMultipart ETag as a string\n```\n"]}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "minio_sync_tool.tasks", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "minio_sync_tool.tasks.sync_repo_no_conflict", "xref": {"fqname": "minio_sync_tool.tasks.sync_repo.sync_repo_no_conflict", "project": null}}, {"name": "minio_sync_tool.tasks.upload_repo", "xref": {"fqname": "minio_sync_tool.tasks.sync_repo.upload_repo", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "minio_sync_tool", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "minio_sync_tool.MinioHelper", "xref": {"fqname": "minio_sync_tool.minio_helper.MinioHelper", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "minio_sync_tool.tasks.sync_repo", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "minio_sync_tool.tasks.sync_repo.lock_repo", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "local_repo", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "minio_sync_tool.tasks.sync_repo.unlock_repo", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "local_repo", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "minio_sync_tool.tasks.sync_repo.get_localized_datetime", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "datetime_str", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": 